<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.2">
<l>intiraṉ pirama ṉīcaṉeṉ ṟivarka ḷeṇṇilpal kuṇaṅkaḷē yiyaṟṟa</l>
<l>tantaiyun tāyum makkaḷum mikka cuṟṟamuñ cuṟṟiniṉ ṟakalāp</l>
<l>pantamum panta maṟuppatōr maruntum pāṉmaiyum palluyirk kellām</l>
<l>antamum vāḻvu māyavem perumā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam is our great lord</l>
<l>Who became the bonds of father, mother, children,</l>
<l rend="indent">and many relations which do not vanish, continuously surrounding [us],</l>
<l>[And] the cure for severing the bonds [of worldly life], [innate] being,</l>
<l rend="indent">all the destruction of many lives and [their] existing,</l>
<l>So that those called Indra, Brahmā, and Īśa compose</l>
<l rend="indent">[praises of his] many countless qualities.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
